00:23:08,952 --> 00:23:13,184
奥多纳，你能…
Odona, can you...

328
00:23:13,256 --> 00:23:16,748
记得为什么你们的人会梦想独处吗？
remember why your people dream of being alone?

329
00:23:19,195 --> 00:23:23,461
- 因为他们永远不可能  - 为什么？
- Because they never can be. - Why?

330
00:23:28,605 --> 00:23:31,768
是什么让独处如此不可能？
What makes it so impossible to be alone?

331
00:23:33,243 --> 00:23:37,077
因为我们人太多了，太多了
Because there are so many of us. So many.

332
00:23:37,147 --> 00:23:40,583
没有位置，
There is no place,

333
00:23:40,650 --> 00:23:43,278
没有街道，没有房子，
no street, no house,

334
00:23:43,353 --> 00:23:46,288
没有花园，没有海滩
no garden, no beach,

335
00:23:46,356 --> 00:23:50,258
没有没有人的山
no mountain that is not filled with people.

336
00:23:50,326 --> 00:23:52,294
我们每个人都会杀人
Each one of us would kill...

337
00:23:52,362 --> 00:23:57,299
为了找到一个属于自己的地方而
in order to find a place alone to himself.

338
00:23:57,367 --> 00:24:00,530
他们愿意为此而死
Yet would willingly die for it,

339
00:24:00,603 --> 00:24:02,628
如果可以的话
if they could.

340
00:24:09,679 --> 00:24:12,705
谁派你来的？
Who sent you here?

341
00:24:12,782 --> 00:24:14,807
没有人命令奥多纳
No one commands Odona!

342
00:24:14,884 --> 00:24:17,512
我不是被派到这里的
I was not sent here.

343
00:24:20,757 --> 00:24:22,748
你是来杀人的？
You have come to kill?

344
00:24:27,731 --> 00:24:31,531
奥多纳，你是来死的吗？
Odona, have you come to die?

345
00:24:34,437 --> 00:24:37,497
我不知道，我不在乎
I don't know. I don't care!

346
00:24:38,608 --> 00:24:41,543
我只知道我在这里
I only know I'm here.

347
00:24:41,611 --> 00:24:44,171
我只知道我很开心
I only know I'm happy.

348
00:25:25,550 --> 00:25:27,848
现在我所要做的就是找到一个医疗箱，
Now, all I have to do is find a medical kit,

349
00:25:27,919 --> 00:25:30,911
我可以完全治愈它
and I can completely cure this.

350
00:25:30,989 --> 00:25:34,447
- 治愈？  - 是的，发炎会消失
- Cure? - Yes, the irritation would be gone.

351
00:25:34,526 --> 00:25:37,461
如果你没有找到会发生什么？
What will happen if you do not find one?

352
00:25:37,529 --> 00:25:39,463
你会生病并死去吗？
Will you become sick and die?

353
00:25:39,531 --> 00:25:42,591
哦，不，这么小的伤不会
Oh, no. Over something as simple as this?

354
00:25:42,667 --> 00:25:45,568
不，它最终会自行痊愈，但是…
No, It'll cure itself eventually, but

355
00:25:49,708 --> 00:25:51,642
你知道吗，
Do you know, uh

356
00:25:51,710 --> 00:25:55,441
我甚至不记得这是怎么发生的
I don't even remember how this happened.

357
00:25:55,514 --> 00:25:58,415
[连续轻击声] 
[Soft Thrumming] 

358
00:25:58,483 --> 00:26:00,815
你听到了吗？
Do you hear that?

359
00:26:00,886 --> 00:26:04,515
是的，听起来像一个引擎
Yes. It sounds like an engine.

360
00:26:04,589 --> 00:26:06,523
不
No.

361
00:26:06,591 --> 00:26:09,924
这艘飞船的引擎不会发出那种声音
The ship's engines don't make that kind of sound.

362
00:26:09,995 --> 00:26:13,362
但是设备有问题，会是这样吗？
But there is something wrong with the equipment. Could that be it?

363
00:26:13,431 --> 00:26:16,127
我知道这艘船可能发出的每一种声音
I know every sound that this ship might make.

364
00:26:17,836 --> 00:26:21,101
那是外面传来的
That's coming from outside.

365
00:26:21,173 --> 00:26:24,301
- 一场风暴…  - 有可能是风暴
- A storm might... - A storm might

366
00:26:25,744 --> 00:26:29,077
但是你听不到它
But you wouldn't be able to hear it.

367
00:26:29,147 --> 00:26:31,342
来吧
Come on.

368
00:26:37,822 --> 00:26:40,382
这是一个观景台，我们能看到外面
This is a viewing port. We'll be able to see outside.

369
00:26:40,458 --> 00:26:44,087
如果有风暴，我们将能够看到它
If there's a storm, we'll be able to see it.

370
00:26:45,709 --> 00:26:47,356
如果行得通
If it works.

371
00:27:00,966 --> 00:27:04,715
人，人的面孔
People. The faces of people!

372
00:27:06,133 --> 00:27:09,310
然后是星星
And then the stars.

373
00:27:13,694 --> 00:27:17,289
发生了什么？外面有什么？
What's happening? What's out there?

374
00:27:17,963 --> 00:27:20,261
[轻击声停止] 
[Thrumming Stops] 

375
00:27:26,471 --> 00:27:30,567
声音没了
The sound is gone.

376
00:27:30,642 --> 00:27:32,576
像那些人的心跳
It was like the heartbeat of all those people,

377
00:27:32,644 --> 00:27:36,774
还有成千上万的人，压在船上
and thousands upon thousands more, pressing against the ship.

378
00:27:39,477 --> 00:27:41,877
但你说我们正在穿越太空
But you said we were moving through space.

379
00:27:42,659 --> 00:27:44,155
是的，我说过
Yes, I said that.

380
00:27:44,155 --> 00:27:46,123
那么人们不可能在外面
Then the people can't be out there.

381
00:27:46,902 --> 00:27:48,343
是的他们可以
Yes, they can.

382
00:27:49,241 --> 00:27:50,790
请不要吓唬我
Please don't frighten me.

383
00:27:55,767 --> 00:28:00,431
这可能是海市蜃楼，它们可能存在于我们的脑海中
It could be a mirage. They could exist in our minds.

384
00:28:00,505 --> 00:28:02,439
你的意思是我们要疯了
You mean that we're going mad.

385
00:28:05,176 --> 00:28:09,408
或者某种力量正在我们的脑海中
Or some power is creating the illusion in our minds...

386
00:28:09,481 --> 00:28:12,450
制造我们离你们星球很近的错觉
that we are somewhere near your planet.

387
00:28:16,321 --> 00:28:18,255
但为什么？
But why?

388
00:28:19,293 --> 00:28:20,898
我不知道
I don't know.

389
00:28:23,019 --> 00:28:24,651
我不知道
I don't know!

390
00:28:32,904 --> 00:28:36,101
我想我知道是怎么回事了
I think I have an idea

391
00:28:36,174 --> 00:28:38,665
这样我们就不会一直试图找出我们在哪里
so that we won't keep trying to find out where we are:

392
00:28:38,743 --> 00:28:41,541
我们会满足于留在这里
that we'll be content to stay here!

393
00:28:41,613 --> 00:28:45,071
哦，知足！
Oh, be content!

394
00:28:46,584 --> 00:28:49,576
知足？
Be content?

395
00:28:49,654 --> 00:28:52,521
知足！
Be content!

396
00:28:52,590 --> 00:28:54,524
除非我发现我的船员发生了什么事
Not until I find out what happened to my crew.

397
00:28:54,592 --> 00:28:56,787
- 他们死了吗？  - 我不知道
- Are they dead? - I don't know.

398
00:28:56,861 --> 00:29:00,763
你杀了他们，这样你就可以将船占为己有了吗？
Did you kill them so you could have the ship to yourself?

399
00:29:00,832 --> 00:29:02,766
舰长…
Captain.

400
00:29:04,769 --> 00:29:07,067
舰长
Captain,

401
00:29:07,138 --> 00:29:09,868
我不对劲
something's happening to me.

402
00:29:09,941 --> 00:29:13,206
我以前从未有过这种感觉，
I never felt like this before.

403
00:29:13,278 --> 00:29:16,611
我以前也从未有过这种感觉
I've never felt like this before either.

404
00:29:16,681 --> 00:29:19,912
这是人们
Is this the way one looks...

405
00:29:19,984 --> 00:29:23,511
生病时的样子吗？
when one is developing a sickness?

406
00:29:26,715 --> 00:29:29,285
你的星球上没有疾病，记得吗？
There's no sickness on your planet, remember?

407
00:29:34,792 --> 00:29:38,228
现在会有了，会有疾病
Now there will be. There will be sickness.

408
00:29:40,605 --> 00:29:43,165
会有死亡
There will be death.

409
00:30:15,093 --> 00:30:17,459
[开门] 
[Door Opening] 

410
00:30:22,097 --> 00:30:24,725
- 霍丁  - 是的，柯克舰长
- Hodin! - Yes, Captain Kirk.

411
00:30:24,800 --> 00:30:27,394
我们的实验已经通过了第一阶段
Our experiment has passed the first stage.

412
00:30:27,469 --> 00:30:30,529
让我进去，我可以帮她
Let me in there. I can help her.

413
00:30:30,606 --> 00:30:34,474
- 我们不需要你的药  - 但她病了
- We have no need of your medicines. - But she's ill!

414
00:30:34,543 --> 00:30:37,842
我们为她的病感谢你
And we're grateful to you for her illness.

415
00:30:37,913 --> 00:30:40,848
你做得很好，我的女儿
You have done well, my daughter.

416
00:30:48,577 --> 00:30:50,545
好好保护舰长，
Guard the captain well.

417
00:30:50,859 --> 00:30:53,851
我们将需要他很长时间
We shall need him for a long time.

418
00:31:09,748 --> 00:31:12,649
我深表同情，但星际舰队
I sympathize deeply, but Starfleet...

419
00:31:12,717 --> 00:31:15,151
不能无视联邦指令
cannot override Federation directives in this matter.

420
00:31:15,220 --> 00:31:18,121
上将，船员们不会明白的
Admiral, the crew will not understand it.

421
00:31:18,189 --> 00:31:21,886
你的船员有兴趣挑起战争吗？
Has your crew suddenly become interested in provoking a war?

422
00:31:21,960 --> 00:31:23,894
这不是星际舰队的使命
That is not Starfleet's mission.

423
00:31:24,151 --> 00:31:26,925
我们只想救舰长的命
We wish only to save the life of the captain.

424
00:31:27,116 --> 00:31:29,311
你没有就此事向联邦
You have not proved your case to the Federation,

425
00:31:29,311 --> 00:31:31,370
或星际舰队证明你的情况
or to Starfleet, for that matter.

426
00:31:31,447 --> 00:31:34,714
我确信我可以做到让您满意，上将
I am positive that I can do so to your satisfaction, Admiral.

427
00:31:35,000 --> 00:31:38,576
从我第一次与大使交流，就一直确信
I have been convinced, since my first exchange with the ambassador,

428
00:31:38,957 --> 00:31:40,988
船长被俘虏了
that the captain has been taken prisoner.

429
00:31:41,056 --> 00:31:42,771
已证明是事实，史波克先生，
Granted as fact, Mr. Spock.

430
00:31:43,033 --> 00:31:45,920
我现在知道他被关押在哪里了
I now know where the captain is being held,

431
00:31:45,994 --> 00:31:49,517
如果他被关押在我们传送他去的同一个地方
if he is being held at the same place to which we transported him.

432
00:31:49,779 --> 00:31:52,968
他们不会在议会厅伤害他
They would not dare harm him in the Gideon council chamber.

433
00:31:53,212 --> 00:31:57,670
长官，他没有被关押在议会厅，
Sir, the captain is not being held in the Gideon council chamber.

434
00:31:57,908 --> 00:32:01,818
- 他被关在附近  - 你回答了是什么和在哪里，
- He is being held nearby. - You have answered what and where.

435
00:32:02,077 --> 00:32:04,602
我在等你解释为什么
I'm waiting for your explanation of why.

436
00:32:04,680 --> 00:32:07,410
因为，星球被我们的传感器屏蔽了
Since the planet is shielded from our sensors,

437
00:32:07,483 --> 00:32:10,884
如果不进行调查，我们就无法确定这一点
we cannot establish that without on-the-spot investigation.

438
00:32:10,953 --> 00:32:13,285
你有证据表明舰长的生命受到威胁吗？
Do you have evidence the captain's life is threatened?

439
00:32:16,592 --> 00:32:19,152
- 拒绝  - 上将
- Permission denied. - Admiral,

440
00:32:19,228 --> 00:32:22,857
我谨正式指出，你的决定是武断的
I wish to state for the record that your decision is arbitrary.

441
00:32:22,931 --> 00:32:24,865
以上
So noted.

442
00:32:30,272 --> 00:32:31,734
会持续很长时间吗？
Will it last long?

443
00:32:33,442 --> 00:32:37,674
这取决于感染者的实力
That depends on the strength of the one infected.

444
00:32:37,746 --> 00:32:40,647
你有很大的力量
You have great strength.

445
00:32:41,750 --> 00:32:45,709
你怎么知道我什么时候死？
How will you know when I am to die?

446
00:32:45,787 --> 00:32:48,984
你的体温会很高
Your body temperature will be very great.

447
00:32:49,057 --> 00:32:52,584
你会看到我们，但你不会知道我们是谁
You will see us, but you will not know who we are.

448
00:32:52,661 --> 00:32:56,461
- 我必须在那之前见到他，父亲  - 休息，现在躺着别动
- I must see him before then, Father. - Rest. Now lie still.

449
00:33:02,538 --> 00:33:04,438
你感到巨大的痛苦吗？
Do you feel great pain?

450
00:33:04,506 --> 00:33:07,805
是的
Yes,

451
00:33:07,876 --> 00:33:10,902
我的手臂和大腿
in my arms and thighs.

452
00:33:10,979 --> 00:33:13,607
感到疼痛是什么感觉？
What is it like to feel pain?

453
00:33:15,286 --> 00:33:16,895
它就像是…
It is like...

454
00:33:19,621 --> 00:33:24,285
…就像当你看到人们对幸福没有希望时，父亲
like when you see the people have no hope for happiness, Father.

455
00:33:25,928 --> 00:33:28,863
你感到非常绝望
You feel great despair,

456
00:33:28,931 --> 00:33:30,990
你的心情很沉重，
and your heart is heavy,

457
00:33:31,066 --> 00:33:34,194
因为你知道你无能为力
because you know you can do nothing.

458
00:33:34,269 --> 00:33:36,203
痛苦就是这样
Pain is like that.

459
00:33:38,173 --> 00:33:40,971
你的勇气使我感到无比自豪
Your courage gives me great pride.

460
00:33:54,002 --> 00:33:55,715
- 让我看看她  - 还不行
- Let me see her. - Not yet.

461
00:33:56,955 --> 00:33:58,344
你不知道她可能有什么病
You don't know what she may have.

462
00:33:58,344 --> 00:34:01,924
但我们知道，她患有纯素脉络丛脑膜炎
But we do. She has Vegan-choriomeningitis.

463
00:34:03,145 --> 00:34:06,419
这是罕见且致命的，如果不在24小时内治疗，
That's very rare, and always fatal if not treated within 24 hours.

464
00:34:06,491 --> 00:34:07,860
我知道，它几乎要了我的命
I know. It almost killed me.

465
00:34:07,930 --> 00:34:11,307
是的，我们的总理在我们的谈判中了解到
Yes. Our prime minister learned about you during our negotiations.

466
00:34:11,378 --> 00:34:13,443
这就是我们带你来这里的原因
That's why we brought you here.

467
00:34:13,519 --> 00:34:17,730
你的血液提供了感染她的微生物
Your blood provided the micro organisms which infected her.

468
00:34:17,803 --> 00:34:19,743
我的手臂就是这样受伤的
That's how my arm got hurt.

469
00:34:19,811 --> 00:34:24,125
是的，正如奥多纳告诉你的，我们这里不需要医生
Yes, as Odona told you, we have no need for medical practitioners here.

470
00:34:24,196 --> 00:34:28,738
很抱歉，伤害了你使我们感到非常不安
Our apologies. We were unforgivably awkward to have hurt you.

471
00:34:42,484 --> 00:34:44,116
你疯了
You're mad.

472
00:34:44,191 --> 00:34:48,071
不，我们很绝望
No. We are desperate.

473
00:34:48,614 --> 00:34:50,092
我不明白
I don't understand...

474
00:34:50,159 --> 00:34:54,770
星际舰队怎么能不允许我们传送下去寻找舰长
how Starfleet can deny permission to beam down to search for the captain.

475
00:34:54,842 --> 00:34:57,181
他们不求我们理解，医生
They did not ask for our understanding, Doctor.

476
00:34:57,251 --> 00:34:59,287
他们怎么能要求我们
I don't see how they expect us to sit here...

477
00:34:59,361 --> 00:35:00,970
坐等着船长再次出现呢？
and wait for the captain to reappear.

478
00:35:01,044 --> 00:35:04,496
不幸的是，我必须违反星际舰队的直接命令
Unfortunately, I must violate a direct order from Starfleet.

479
00:35:04,573 --> 00:35:07,070
这是最好的决定，史波克，我和你一起
That's the best possible decision you could make, Spock. I'm with you.

480
00:35:07,147 --> 00:35:09,059
我不会掉以轻心，医生
I do not make it lightly, Doctor.

481
00:35:09,126 --> 00:35:11,792
然而，指挥部知道霍丁大使
However, Command knows that Ambassador Hodin...

482
00:35:11,864 --> 00:35:14,203
一直没有对我们说实话
has not been totally honest with us.

483
00:35:14,272 --> 00:35:19,209
乌乎拉上尉，重复原始吉迪恩坐标用以传送
Lieutenant Uhura, repeat original Gideon coordinates for beam down.

484
00:35:19,286 --> 00:35:23,763
875，020，079
875, 020, 079.

485
00:35:23,839 --> 00:35:26,144
斯科特先生，给你的坐标呢？
Mr. Scott, coordinates given you?

486
00:35:26,213 --> 00:35:30,228
875，020，709
875, 020, 709.

487
00:35:30,303 --> 00:35:33,261
坐标不匹配
Coordinates don't match.

488
00:35:33,338 --> 00:35:37,848
正是，我会立刻传送下去，斯科特先生，你来掌舵
Precisely. I shall beam down at once. Mr. Scott, you have the con.

489
00:35:37,923 --> 00:35:40,386
我去哪我的医疗三录仪，在传送室和你见面
I'll pick up my medical tricorder, meet you in the transporter room.

490
00:35:40,463 --> 00:35:42,701
不行，医生，我不能承担
Negative, Doctor. I cannot accept the responsibility...

491
00:35:42,772 --> 00:35:46,170
命令官员违反指令的责任
for ordering a fellow officer to violate a Starfleet directive.

492
00:35:46,237 --> 00:35:48,768
我只能为自己做决定
I can make such a decision only for myself.

493
00:35:48,842 --> 00:35:51,373
我不是要你替我做决定
I'm not asking you to make the decision for me.

494
00:35:51,447 --> 00:35:54,507
形势迫使我这样做，医生
The situation forces me to do so, Doctor.

495
00:35:54,770 --> 00:35:57,910
在这种情况下，这是你能做出的最糟糕的决定
In that case, it's the worst possible decision you can make.

496
00:35:58,649 --> 00:36:00,679
这不会花很长时间
This will not take long.

497
00:36:05,610 --> 00:36:10,356
这不就是柯克舰长离开前说的话吗？
Isn't that just about what Captain Kirk said before he left?

498
00:36:31,341 --> 00:36:33,511
柯克舰长
Captain Kirk.

499
00:36:33,511 --> 00:36:35,413
我是史波克，柯克舰长？
Spock here. Captain Kirk!

500
00:36:46,416 --> 00:36:49,284
[仪器嗡嗡声] 
[ Instrument Humming ] 

501
00:37:03,602 --> 00:37:06,701
你给联邦的报告是一堆谎言
Your report to the Federation was a tissue of lies.

502
00:37:06,777 --> 00:37:12,456
你把吉迪恩的环境，物理，文化条件
You described environmental, physical, cultural conditions...

503
00:37:12,456 --> 00:37:14,360
- 描述得像天堂一样  - 本来确实如此，
- that would make Gideon a paradise. - And so it was!

504
00:37:14,431 --> 00:37:19,137
很久以前，我们所描述的都是真实的
A long, long time ago what we described was true!

505
00:37:19,209 --> 00:37:22,913
吉迪恩的大气一直是无菌的
The atmosphere on Gideon has always been germfree.

506
00:37:22,986 --> 00:37:28,091
人们在身体和精神上的完美中茁壮成长
And the people flourished in their physical and spiritual perfection.

507
00:37:28,167 --> 00:37:32,007
最终，甚至寿命也增加了
Eventually, even the life span increased.

508
00:37:32,078 --> 00:37:36,818
死亡对我们来说几乎是陌生的
Death became almost unknown to us.

509
00:37:36,890 --> 00:37:41,028
只有当身体不再能够自我再生时才会发生
It occurred only when the body could no longer regenerate itself.

510
00:37:41,102 --> 00:37:44,908
现在这种情况只发生在非常老的人身上
And that happens now only to the very old.

511
00:37:44,979 --> 00:37:47,919
这是大多数人都会羡慕的条件
Those are conditions most people would envy.

512
00:37:47,987 --> 00:37:50,724
但吉迪恩人并不觉得它令人羡慕
But Gideon did not find it enviable.

513
00:37:51,047 --> 00:37:55,104
出生率持续上升，人口增长
The birth rate continued to rise, and the population grew,

514
00:37:55,172 --> 00:37:59,412
直到现在，吉迪恩被包裹在一团生命物质中…
until now Gideon is encased in a living mass...

515
00:37:59,485 --> 00:38:03,930
我们不能休息，没有平安，没有喜乐
who can find no rest, no peace, no joy.

516
00:38:05,568 --> 00:38:08,132
你为什么不引进
Then why haven't you introduced...

517
00:38:08,207 --> 00:38:11,649
男性和女性绝育的新技术？
any of the new techniques to sterilize men and women?

518
00:38:11,717 --> 00:38:15,660
每个器官都会自我更新，这是不可能的
Every organ renews itself. It would be impossible.

519
00:38:15,728 --> 00:38:19,728
那让你的人民了解避孕工具
Then let your people learn about the devices to prevent conception.

520
00:38:19,806 --> 00:38:22,176
联邦将提供你们所需要的一切
The Federation will provide anything you need.

521
00:38:22,245 --> 00:38:27,157
但你明白，吉迪恩人一直相信
But you see, the people of Gideon have always believed...

522
00:38:27,226 --> 00:38:31,225
生命是神圣的
that life is sacred,

523
00:38:31,304 --> 00:38:33,707
对生命的热爱
that the love of life...

524
00:38:33,776 --> 00:38:36,807
是最好的礼物
is the greatest gift.

525
00:38:36,885 --> 00:38:41,454
这是吉迪恩人不可动摇的真理
That is the one unshakable truth of Gideon.

526
00:38:41,530 --> 00:38:44,562
这种压倒性的对生命的热爱
And this overwhelming love of life...

527
00:38:44,638 --> 00:38:48,844
导致了我们的再生能力
has developed our regenerative capacity...

528
00:38:48,917 --> 00:38:50,946
和我们的长寿
and our great longevity.

529
00:38:51,022 --> 00:38:53,861
还有你现在面临的巨大苦难
And the great misery which you now face.

530
00:38:53,930 --> 00:38:56,300
令人痛苦的事实，舰长
That is bitterly true, Captain.

531
00:38:56,370 --> 00:39:01,007
然而，我们不能否认塑造我们进化的真相
Nevertheless, we cannot deny the truth which shaped our evolution.

532
00:39:01,083 --> 00:39:04,525
我们无权干涉
We are incapable of destroying or interfering with...

533
00:39:04,592 --> 00:39:09,629
我们深爱的事物的创造
the creation of that which we love so deeply life...

534
00:39:09,706 --> 00:39:13,979
从胎儿到发育的生命，各种形式的生命
in every form, from fetus to developed being.

535
00:39:14,051 --> 00:39:18,688
它违背了我们的传统，违背了我们的本性
It is against our tradition, against our very nature.

536
00:39:20,268 --> 00:39:22,262
我们根本做不到
We simply could not do it.

537
00:39:22,341 --> 00:39:24,369
然而你可以杀死一个年轻的女孩
Yet you can kill a young girl!

538
00:39:24,445 --> 00:39:29,323
我们正试图重新调整整个文明的生命周期
We're trying to readjust the life cycle of an entire civilization.

539
00:39:29,392 --> 00:39:31,454
你在杀死你自己的女儿！
You're killing your own daughter!

540
00:39:31,532 --> 00:39:35,600
我女儿希望让你感受到吉迪恩人的痛苦
My daughter hoped to make you feel the agony of Gideon.

541
00:39:35,676 --> 00:39:37,909
但这是不可能的
But it was impossible.

542
00:39:37,981 --> 00:39:42,084
没有陌生人可以意识到
No stranger could realize...

543
00:39:42,159 --> 00:39:44,997
在这里生命有多恐怖
the horror that life can be here.

544
00:39:45,067 --> 00:39:48,509
我不会乞求你理解我的悲伤
I will not beg for your understanding of my personal grief,

545
00:39:48,578 --> 00:39:52,520
也不会为了获得你的合作​​而夸大它
nor will I parade it for you to gain your cooperation.

546
00:39:52,588 --> 00:39:55,186
我对女儿的爱
My love for my daughter...

547
00:39:55,261 --> 00:39:58,258
太深了，无法表达
is too deep for display.

548
00:39:58,336 --> 00:40:00,467
我对她的骄傲甚至更深
My pride in her runs even deeper.

549
00:40:00,542 --> 00:40:04,541
我女儿自由地选择做她正在做的事情
My daughter freely chose to do what she is doing,

550
00:40:04,620 --> 00:40:08,393
正如吉迪恩人可以自由选择
as the people of Gideon are free to choose.

551
00:40:10,837 --> 00:40:14,837
你需要的病毒非常罕见，
The virus you need is very rare.

552
00:40:14,915 --> 00:40:16,114
谁来提供？
Who will provide it?

553
00:40:19,360 --> 00:40:23,324
你会留下来，你的血液会提供它
You will stay. Your blood will provide it.

554
00:40:23,403 --> 00:40:25,341
不，先生，不是我，
Oh, no, sir, not me.

555
00:40:25,409 --> 00:40:28,281
你有很多方法可用 我只提到了几个，
You have many methods available. I've mentioned only a few.

556
00:40:30,021 --> 00:40:34,124
我不会为此目的献出我的生命，我有很多计划，
I do not offer my life for this purpose. I have many plans.

557
00:40:34,199 --> 00:40:38,575
我对奥多纳抱有希望，不是死亡
And I have hopes other than death for Odona.

558
00:40:38,645 --> 00:40:42,051
我女儿恳求你留下来
My daughter pleaded with you to stay.

559
00:40:42,120 --> 00:40:44,319
我们之间所说的
What was said...

560
00:40:44,393 --> 00:40:47,664
和发生的一切都别让人知道
and what happened between us was for us alone.

561
00:40:47,735 --> 00:40:52,443
她希望你会爱她并想要留下来
She hoped you would love her and wish to stay.

562
00:40:52,515 --> 00:40:54,988
所以这就是你的计划
So that was your plan

563
00:40:55,055 --> 00:40:58,759
我会被她的魔咒所迷惑
that I would fall so under her spell...

564
00:40:58,831 --> 00:41:01,269
我会放弃我的自由，
that I would give up my freedom...

565
00:41:01,338 --> 00:41:05,372
成为一个自愿的牺牲品
and become a willing sacrifice.

566
00:41:05,449 --> 00:41:08,822
和我们在一起，我们很绝望
Stay with us. We're desperate.

567
00:41:12,300 --> 00:41:14,796
[哔哔] 
[Communicator Beeps] 

568
00:41:17,983 --> 00:41:19,920
奥多纳的体温在上升，
Odona's fever is rising.

569
00:41:21,626 --> 00:41:24,532
她在呼唤詹姆斯·柯克的名字
She's calling the name of James Kirk.

570
00:41:27,409 --> 00:41:30,280
你看，你现在不能离开我们
You see, you cannot leave us now.

571
00:41:33,358 --> 00:41:35,295
去找她
Go to her.

572
00:42:06,615 --> 00:42:09,680
企业号的
Exact duplicate...

573
00:42:09,752 --> 00:42:12,144
精确复制品
of the Enterprise.

574
00:42:19,924 --> 00:42:23,309
但完全无法运行
But completely inoperative.

575
00:42:39,332 --> 00:42:42,449
史波克呼叫企业号，史波克呼叫企业号
Spock to Enterprise. Spock to Enterprise.

576
00:42:43,195 --> 00:42:44,739
我是斯科特，史波克先生
Scott here, Mr. Spock.

577
00:42:44,739 --> 00:42:47,805
我在企业号的舰桥上和你通话
I am speaking to you from the bridge of the Enterprise.

578
00:42:49,811 --> 00:42:51,200
你在哪儿？
You're where?

579
00:42:51,267 --> 00:42:54,530
在企业号的舰桥上，斯科特先生
On the bridge of the Enterprise, Mr. Scott.

580
00:42:54,596 --> 00:42:57,564
那些是你强调的坐标
Those were the coordinates you insisted on.

581
00:42:57,637 --> 00:42:59,513
它们是对的，
And they were correct.

582
00:42:59,578 --> 00:43:03,481
我在企业号的精确复制品上
I am on board an exact duplicate of the Enterprise.

583
00:43:04,203 --> 00:43:07,074
企业号的精确复制品？
An exact duplicate of the Enterprise?

584
00:43:07,147 --> 00:43:09,076
它在轨道上吗，史波克先生？
Is it in orbit, Mr. Spock?

585
00:43:09,152 --> 00:43:11,181
在轨道上，医生？
In orbit, Doctor?

586
00:43:12,134 --> 00:43:13,129
从某种意义上说，
In a manner of speaking.

587
00:43:14,098 --> 00:43:18,051
吉迪恩在轨道上，而飞船在吉迪恩上
Gideon is in orbit, and the ship is on Gideon.

588
00:43:18,548 --> 00:43:22,078
一个好的开始，舰长呢？
Well, that's a beginning, but what about the captain?

589
00:43:22,250 --> 00:43:24,180
我确定他在某个地方，
I'm sure he's on board somewhere.

590
00:43:24,255 --> 00:43:28,191
我在收集生命读数，通话完毕
I'm picking up life readings. Spock out.

591
00:43:28,923 --> 00:43:32,539
[史波克] ：舰船日志，星历5423.8，
[ Spock's Voice ] Ship's Log: Star date 5423.8.

592
00:43:32,610 --> 00:43:34,837
史波克大副报告
First Officer Spock reporting.

593
00:43:34,907 --> 00:43:37,387
很明显，吉迪恩人将柯克舰长传送到了
Obviously the Gideon's have transported Captain Kirk...

594
00:43:37,462 --> 00:43:41,597
企业号的复制品上，迷惑他的头脑，
onto this replica of the Enterprise to so confuse his mind...

595
00:43:41,666 --> 00:43:45,350
使他容易受到一些实验的影响
as to make him susceptible to some extraordinary experiment.

596
00:43:45,418 --> 00:43:48,551
我的目的是找到舰长
It is my intention to locate the captain and warn him...

597
00:43:48,621 --> 00:43:52,921
并在实验结束前警告他，逻辑表明
before the experiment reaches its conclusion, which logic indicates...

598
00:43:52,987 --> 00:43:56,956
一旦舰长知道，就意味着他生命的终结
means the end of the captain's life as he knows it.

599
00:43:57,029 --> 00:44:00,680
[呻吟] 
[ Moaning ] 

600
00:44:05,682 --> 00:44:08,522
请允许我把麦考伊医生带下来，
If you don't allow me to bring Dr. McCoy down here,

601
00:44:08,588 --> 00:44:10,972
否则来不及给她做任何治疗了
it'll soon be too late to do anything for her.

602
00:44:11,046 --> 00:44:13,853
我们已经告诉过你，她和我的愿望是
We have told you, it is her wish and mine...

603
00:44:13,919 --> 00:44:16,761
不要干扰病毒的自然过程
that there be no interference with the natural progress of the virus.

604
00:44:16,825 --> 00:44:18,706
她的死是不必要的
Her death is unnecessary.

605
00:44:18,772 --> 00:44:20,677
如果她活着，她的血液将提供
Even if she lives, her blood will provide...

606
00:44:20,751 --> 00:44:22,786
你需要的与我相同的血清
the same serum you need as mine would.

607
00:44:22,858 --> 00:44:26,712
不，她的英年早逝
No. Her death at so young an age...

608
00:44:26,785 --> 00:44:30,966
能让人们相信我们的生命周期是可以改变的
will let the people know for certain that our life cycle can be changed.

609
00:44:31,032 --> 00:44:35,212
这个象征将培养出敬业的年轻志愿者
It's the symbol that'll bring forth the dedicated young volunteers.

610
00:44:35,569 --> 00:44:40,491
他们新血液中的血清会改变吉迪恩
The serum in their new blood will change Gideon,

611
00:44:40,740 --> 00:44:43,649
它将再次成为曾经的天堂
and it will, once more, be the paradise it was.

612
00:44:43,649 --> 00:44:44,668
[呻吟] 
[Moaning] 

613
00:45:07,011 --> 00:45:09,820
我很高兴你在这里
I'm glad that you are here.

614
00:45:11,270 --> 00:45:13,121
我的时间还多吗？
Is the time short?

615
00:45:14,833 --> 00:45:18,021
不多了
Very short.

616
00:45:18,877 --> 00:45:22,578
我请求你让我们的旅程永远持续下去
And I asked you to make our journey last forever.

617
00:45:25,590 --> 00:45:29,323
它在这里开始
Oh. It began here.

618
00:45:31,256 --> 00:45:34,343
它可以继续
And it can continue.

619
00:45:34,417 --> 00:45:37,136
只要你允许，
If only you'll allow me,

620
00:45:37,219 --> 00:45:40,084
我就能治愈你
I can cure you.

621
00:45:41,172 --> 00:45:44,003
我不害怕会发生的事
I'm not afraid of what will happen.

622
00:45:44,084 --> 00:45:47,070
只是现在…
It is just that now...

623
00:45:47,369 --> 00:45:52,245
我全心全意地想永远和你在一起
I wish with all my heart to stay with you forever.

624
00:46:33,760 --> 00:46:35,678
阁下，
Your Excellency.

625
00:46:35,923 --> 00:46:39,752
舰长，你看起来不错，星际舰队的分析是正确的
Captain, you're looking well. Starfleet's analysis was correct.

626
00:46:39,752 --> 00:46:43,630
史波克先生，我们有个病人给麦考伊医生，让斯科提传送我们上去
Mr. Spock, we have a patient for Dr. McCoy. Have Scotty beam us up.

627
00:46:45,324 --> 00:46:48,523
史波克呼叫企业号，史波克呼叫企业号
Spock to Enterprise. Spock to Enterprise.

628
00:46:48,915 --> 00:46:51,975
- 我是斯科特  - 三个人要传送，斯科特先生
- Scott here. - Three to beam up, Mr. Scott.

629
00:46:52,051 --> 00:46:53,824
- 相同的坐标？- 不是，
- Same coordinates? - Negative.

630
00:46:53,824 --> 00:46:57,317
锁定我的通讯器信号
Lock in on my communicator signal.

631
00:46:58,473 --> 00:47:02,326
阁下，请不要干涉
Your Excellency, please do not interfere.

632
00:47:02,326 --> 00:47:06,796
我已经有了一个需要与高层解决的严重问题
I already have one serious problem to resolve with upper echelons.

633
00:47:26,737 --> 00:47:30,610
嗯，真险，但你挺过来了
Well, it was close, but you made it.

634
00:47:30,678 --> 00:47:32,433
我痊愈了？
I am cured?

635
00:47:32,433 --> 00:47:35,049
对，就像舰长一样
Right, just like the captain.

636
00:47:39,499 --> 00:47:42,732
你应该愤怒地大喊，而不是微笑
Instead of smiling at me, you should be shouting in anger.

637
00:47:42,807 --> 00:47:45,004
为什么，因为你又好了？
Why? Because you're well again?

638
00:47:45,809 --> 00:47:49,644
不，因为我假装…
No. Because I pretended to be

639
00:47:52,493 --> 00:47:56,126
你怎么还能忍受看我，在我那样骗你之后？
How can you bear to look at me after the way I deceived you?

640
00:47:56,201 --> 00:48:00,837
至少你欠我让我看你的特权
At least you owe me the privilege of letting me look at you.

641
00:48:06,857 --> 00:48:09,225
你真是个绅士，柯克舰长
You are a gentleman, Captain Kirk.

642
00:48:09,296 --> 00:48:11,925
谢谢你，女士
Thank you, ma'am.

643
00:48:12,002 --> 00:48:14,130
吉迪恩不再需要你了，
You are no longer needed on Gideon.

644
00:48:14,206 --> 00:48:16,904
我可以代替你在那里
I can take your place there.

645
00:48:18,726 --> 00:48:20,419
这是你想做的吗？
Is that what you wanted?

646
00:48:23,325 --> 00:48:25,819
那是我必须做的
That is what I must do.

647
00:48:25,897 --> 00:48:27,891
现在那里需要我
I am needed there now.

648
00:48:32,971 --> 00:48:36,000
到处都需要你，奥多纳
You're needed everywhere, Odona.

649
00:48:48,779 --> 00:48:50,694
它不像我们的船
It is not like our ship.

650
00:48:50,762 --> 00:48:53,433
哦，不，完全一样，只是这艘能飞
Oh, yes, it is. It's exactly the same. Only this one works.

651
00:48:53,504 --> 00:48:55,421
它去过许多其他星球？
It goes to many other planets?

652
00:48:55,488 --> 00:48:59,906
是的，整个银河系，还有一个区别，
Yes, it goes to the whole galaxy, with another difference

653
00:48:59,982 --> 00:49:02,227
这艘有很多人
this one is crowded.

654
00:49:02,297 --> 00:49:05,465
对你来说似乎很拥挤？
It seems crowded to you?

655
00:49:05,537 --> 00:49:07,946
现在确实如此
It does now.

656
00:49:09,735 --> 00:49:13,159
你要留在船上吗？
Are you going to stay on the ship?

657
00:49:13,236 --> 00:49:16,143
是的，奥多纳，我必须这样做
Yes, Odona, I have to.

658
00:49:17,798 --> 00:49:20,264
尽管我的星球如此拥挤，
As crowded as my planet is,

659
00:49:20,344 --> 00:49:24,998
但我希望它能再容纳一个人
I could wish for it to hold one more person.

660
00:49:28,242 --> 00:49:33,134
柯克呼叫传送控制，传送一个人到吉迪恩星球
Kirk to transporter control. One to beam down to the planet Gideon.

661
00:49:36,143 --> 00:49:38,982
我会想念你的，詹姆斯·柯克舰长
I will miss you, Captain James Kirk.

